{"word":"κυβεύω","slug":"κυβεύω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>κυβεύω</b></el> <el>(κῠβεύω,) ( φυτ. <el>-σω</el>) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:κύβος'><el>κύβος</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>to play at dice</i>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><a href='S:metaphorically'>metaph.</a> <i>to run a risk</i> or <i>hazard</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a>; <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a> <i>to hazard, venture on</i>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>:—<a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> <i>to be set upon a stake</i>, <b><a href='S:Anthology'>Anth.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}